The paper deals with the computational automation of literature review, which involves the analysis of unstructured data. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper focuses on the extraction of latent relationships from unstructured text, which could also fall under the sub-category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
